last_episode_to_air.name: Unknown Dangers
last_episode_to_air.overview: This episode counts down Australia's top ten dangerous animals, including the razor-jawed jack jumper aunt and the beautiful killer box jellyfish.

episodes.name: Risky Waters
episodes.overview: Venomous critters roam both land and sea in Australia. Under the ocean's surface is an entire world of swimmers inflicting pain and paralysis.

episodes.name: Fast and Furious
episodes.overview: Cameras capture creatures with a mean streak and lightening-quick reflexes, including a tiny grub with potent itch power and a giant water buffalo.

episodes.name: Dead or Alive
episodes.overview: From city fliers and ocean swimmers to outback dwellers and even an extinct species, see how this group of beasts ranks on the danger scale.

episodes.name: Tiny Terrors
episodes.overview: Take an insider's look at Australia's most deadly and diminutive species, including a virus-carrying mosquito and the waterhole-dwelling olive python.

episodes.name: The Ancient Killer
episodes.overview: Meet a wild canine with cute puppies and a bad reputation. Learn why the wild dingo may look cuddly, but is a deadly playmate.

episodes.name: The Greatest Fear
episodes.overview: This episode reveals how a soothing dip in Australia's ocean can turn terrifying when the cold eyes and sharp teeth of a shark appear.

episodes.name: Cruel Creatures
episodes.overview: This episode focuses on deadly creatures' playful ways, including the brutal sea lion, the poisonous stonefish and the furry fruit bat.

episodes.name: Instant Death
episodes.overview: This episode focuses on dangerous beasts and their natural weapons: Talons, teeth, fangs and tentacles are all used as instruments of pain and death.

episodes.name: Seeing Red
episodes.overview: Visit with one of Australia's most feared ocean dwellers: The stingray glides through the water, waiting to inflict pain with it's barbed stinger.

episodes.name: Lurking in the Grass
episodes.overview: See how Australia's grasslands harbour animals are worth worrying about, especially the venomous reptiles that slither amongst the country's green fields.

episodes.name: Brutal Bites
episodes.overview: Which beast has the most vicious bite? It might be the jaws of an ancient creature, a rare reptile's fangs or poisonous spines caught on a fish hook.
